description.6: When the day eventually comes, Aunt May wants to be put out of her misery and go without pain. Peter can't bear to hear another word.
description.7: It's the catastrophic conclusion to "Sturm Und Drang: A Story Of Love And War!" With Wakanda on the brink of destruction, and the world on the edge of global conflict, the Black Panther battles to the death with his greatest enemy- Klaw, master of sound! Meanwhile, the fate of the world, and possibly the universe, rests on the narrow shoulders of...Everett K. Ross?
description.8: It's a trial of the soul for Captain America, as the one person closest to Steve Rogers suddenly becomes an enemy!
description.9: It's Spider-Girl and Buzz against the Avengers and Raptor in this action packed issue! Will the old Parker Luck ring true?
description.10: Wolverine gets ferociously feral with Mister X after the villain tries to renounce Logan's claim as "being the best"!
description.11: Magneto's ultimatum is broadcast live for all to see - surrender to his will or be destroyed!
description.13: The Fantastic Four gets trapped in the Negative Zone, but which teammate gets stranded behind? And who are the Nega-Explorers? Plus: after months of scheming, the Gideon Board finally makes their move!'
description.16: Two crime bosses scrambling after an ancient stone tablet team up with none other than super-villain, The Lizard! It's up to Spider-Man to put a stop to the madness!
description.19: Revealed: the secrets of Captain America. Why did the super soldier leave Earth's Mightiest Heroes -- and why can't he return? Find out when The Six collide with the Avengers!
description.22: Spider-Man goes head to head with Jimmy 6 and The Enforcers and we find out where Mary-Jane has been all along...
description.26: Garth Ennis unleashes the Hulk! What hope do mere mortal men have against the most powerful creature to ever walk the planet? Learn the answer as Ennis and John McCrea (Jenny Sparks) look into the minds of the soldiers given the unlucky order of facing the green goliath!
description.32: Collecting Thor #337-348.  Walter Simonson's work on the Mighty Thor swept the Norse God of Thunder to heights never before seen and rarely achieved in his wake. From the majesty and mystery of fabled Asgard to the gritty streets of New York City, Thor was never the same.
description.34: War brews for man and mutant alike. Its origin: Genosha!
description.36: Get ready for some electrifying lightsaber battle action! Aurra Sing arrives on Coruscant with a mean streak, killing Jedi within the very shadows of the Temple. The Jedi Council must now decide how to deal with the infamous bounty hunter. Several Jedi Knights volunteer for the honor of bringing Sing to justice. But do they want justice or vengeance? It's going to take more than a grudge to bring down an assassin with a reputation for killing Jedi.
description.37: As the villainous'Taxer Sundown'prepares to flee'Ord Mantell, a young woman is abducted by monstrous'Mantellian savrips. Hoping to rescue the woman and capture Sundown,'Qui-Gon Jinn'and'Obi-Wan Kenobi'are forced to split up, but their separate paths lead to even more unexpected perils, and a face-off against intergalactic'slavers. Can the two'Jedi'bring justice to the lawless world before time runs out? Find out in the shattering conclusion of'Last Stand on Ord Mantell.
description.40: It's easy to get lost on the high seas of Mon Calamari, and when you're 8-feet tall and covered with hair, that's a prospect second only to Hell... Han, Chewie, and the rest of the Millennium Falcon's passenger list scour the floating city of Mon Ubris for the man who can lead them to the fabled Vassilika of Yavin. Unfortunately his trail leads out across the vast ocean plains towards the mysterious Bank of Knowledge. Bossk and his fellow bounty hunters might want to think twice before crossing their paths, however, as there's not much meaner than a water-logged Wookiee!
description.48: Have you ever had one of those days? Your boss won't stop bothering you with petty complaints? Your teacher won't get off your back about your late book report? The neighbor kids won't stop screaming? Well, escape your everyday troubles with an all new and improved issue of'Star Wars Tales! Join'Boba Fett,'Plo Koon,'Micah Giiett,'Yoda,'Mace Windu, and a fellow named'Domo Jones'as they take your mind off your cares and to a place where you're as likely to run into a three-eyed alien as encounter bureaucratic headaches!'
description.49: Cyclops' companion reveals her true motives - to become the new vessel for Apocalypse! Can Cable and Jean save Scott while also preventing the return of Apocalypse?
description.51: Peter takes a night out with the boys! But of course, the plans never go as planned when Peter sneaks out as Spider-Man multiple times to uncover why a mysterious cat is being hunted by goons.
description.53: Just another day for Spider-Man. Fighting crime, and stopping bank robberies in Times Square!
description.54: The cold war goes hot as the Black Panther and Wakanda face a war with Namor and Atlantis, Magneto and Genosha, Lord Ghaur and the Deviants, and Doctor Doom and Latveria!
description.55: While Cap, Sharon Carter, and Carter's team battle A.I.M. forces, Cap remembers the sacrifice of Bucky Barnes.
description.56: Unable to capture Raptor after their previous encounter, and with a mystery villain still on the loose, it's up to Spider-Girl to save the day...but without her powers!
description.57: Logan uses the Ladykillers T and A as combat practice for his face-off against Mister X.
description.58: Kitty resigns from the X-Men before travelling to Russia to scatter Peter's ashes across his homeland.
description.60: No joke: one of the FF's lives is majorly altered in this issue! The Fantastic Four race to rescue one of their own from the clutches of the Grey Gargoyle, but will their efforts be too little, too late?'
description.63: The demented duo of Garth Ennis (PUNISHER) and John McCrea (Hitman) unleash the green goliath! Meet Patrick D. Mitchell. His father was awarded the Silver Star for his service in Vietnam. His grandfather died during General Patton's drive to the Rhine during WWII. It's even rumored that one of his relatives charged up San Juan Hill with Teddy Roosevelt. Today it's Patrick's turn to face his destiny. For today his Company in the U.S. Army's 29th Infantry will lock and load, say their prayers, and face down the living engine of destruction known as the Hulk. And in the blazing heat of the Nevada desert, Mitchell will feel the cool grip of Death around his throat...and the breath of the strongest creature to ever walk the Earth on his neck. Patrick D. Mitchell is a Lieutenant. But today he just may learn what it means to be a soldier.
description.68: Will Ma Gnucci triumph? Can Detective Soap nail the Punisher? Will Frank join forces with Mr. Payback, the Elite and the Holy? What are the final fates of Spacker Dave and Mr. Bumpo?
description.75: Wolverine is back! Logan, Havok and Jean Grey sneak across enemy lines into Canada on a very personal rescue mission. But how do Sabretooth and Alpha Flight fit into the picture?
description.77: This issue, meet Jedi Yoshi Raph-Elan. On his way to a meeting of Jedi, Yoshi is attacked by an unknown enemy. Stranded without even a lightsaber, he must find out what this new threat wants. Along the way, he meets the beautiful princess Lourdes, and learns a lesson about trusting ancient prophecies.
description.78: Cyclops and Corsair go on a father/son camping trip. What could possibly go wrong?
description.79: Investigating the deaths of a cargo freighter's crew,'Qui-Gon Jinn'and'Obi-Wan Kenobi'travel to a moisture plant on'Ord Mantell. There, they they learn that a ruthless land baron named'Taxer Sundown'may have had ties with the ill-fated freighter. But when they discover that most of the Ord Mantell colonists are convinced that Taxer Sundown is a'Jedi, Qui-Gon and Obi-Wan realize that they might be up against more than they can handle!
description.84: How do the NYPD see Spider-Man? After being involved in many run-ins with the law, including everything from capturing crooks to the death of Captain Stacy, do New York's finest see Spidey as a hero or menace?
description.86: Will there be war between Wakanda and Atlantis? Tensions erupt as the Black Panther, the Sub-Mariner and Doctor Doom play a deadly game of chess! Guest-starring Storm and the Avengers!
description.87: Now that Proticide's deprogramming has worn off, him and Captain America take on A.I.M.!
description.88: Despite her inability to use her Spider powers, May is insistent on proving she can still be a super hero. But when it's time to face off with a big mysterious villain, will she be able to put her money where her mouth is?
description.89: Wolverine is tested by the Major and his henchmen to see if he is worthy of Mister X's "services".
description.90: It's holiday time at the X-Mansion! After so much tragedy, these days represent a time for the mutant family to bond and heal. But Thunderbird is not only shaken by the strange lives his new teammates lead, he is also homesick. Will Neal Shaara remain with the X-Men or return to India? Seeds for the X-Treme X-Men series are planted here!
description.92: Fear the touch of the Grey Gargoyle! His merest gaze can turn you to stone - something that Ben Grimm knows a Thing or two about! What will happen when these two gods of granite collide? And where's the rest of the Fantastic Four?
description.97: Peter Parker digs deeper to find out more about his father while simultaneously fighting the big, bad Squid.

1.text: Immortus' mutant battalion has arrived at Castle Doom! Can Reed Richards hold the horde off? Meanwhile, Thor, Captain Marvel, the Hulk, and the X-Men confront the Supreme Intelligence.

2.text: The X-Men take the fight to Magneto and the Brotherhood, but not without a casualty of war.

4.text: LEARNING CURVE PART 1.  After dispatching of the Shocker, Peter Parker heads to the Daily Bugle looking for a job as a photographer.  But his next big assignment - taking down the Kingpin of Crime as his web-headed alter ego Spider-Man.

5.text: Deadpool and Pool Boy set aside their differences in order to hunt down the murderous Maxy Millions. Can Deadpool still trust his new ward?

12.text: The true identity of Scourge - revealed at last! Dive into the past of the Thunderbolts' most persistent foe! What created the seething vendetta that Scourge holds towards them?

14.text:
"CRAZY LIKE A FOX" pt. 2 (of 4)
Marv has targeted the Shi'ar and the Kree for termination, and they've brought the only force in the universe able to stop him. 
32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$2.99

15.text: The Dark Sisterhood descends on Cable's safe house to assassinate him, but find he may be a harder hit than expected!

16.text: Two crime bosses scrambling after an ancient stone tablet team up with none other than Super Villain, the Lizard! It's up to Spider-Man to put a stop to the madness!

17.text: Groups of mutants are always looking for recruits, but the Promise seem to have a different strategy of acquiring teammates…

18.text: Who is the evil genius behind the recent attacks on the FF? If Namor and the Kree Sentry weren't enough, now our fab foursome must contend with the X-Men, Spider-Man, Doctor Strange and the mutant-hunting Sentinels!

20.text: DD and Spidey, two of your favorite heroes in one book! The web-slinger and the Man Without Fear square off with the unholy mastermind behind the Gang of Four, and when we say "unholy," we mean it! Plus: what has the Black Widow uncovered about the Kingpin?

21.text: Paige ends up in a nightmare-come-true when she is accidentally locked in the school during a security procedure.

23.text: Daredevil's identity is finally revealed to Echo as well as the truth about her father. Her new target: Wilson Fisk!

24.text: SPIDER-MAN & WOLVERINE Spider-Man teams up with Wolverine against Weapon X in Times Square! Plus, what happens when Pete tries to adopt Wolverine's "style" in school?
SPIDER-MAN & WOLVERINE Spider-Man teams up with Wolverine against Weapon X in Times Square! Plus, what happens when Pete tries to adopt Wolverine's "style" in school?

25.text:
Ride along with the Punisher as he makes an unexpected detour -- to the
slammer. Will Frank Castle pay for his crimes? Or will he use his "get
out of jail free" card? And speaking of rides, Dagger and the Black
Widow discover that they no longer have one when Natasha's car is stolen
--the trouble is, the car was made by S.H.I.E.L.D.
Ride along with the Punisher as he makes an unexpected detour -- to the slammer. Will Frank Castle pay for his crimes? Or will he use his "get out of jail free" card?

27.text: The team looks set to engage in a losing battle against Dr. Roman and his Warborgs! Roman's mutate army is unleashed at last.

29.text: Tarene tasks Thor with testing her power and the Odinson happily obliges! Meanwhile, Ulik leads a vicious campaign against Asgard!

30.text: We all know the billionaire behind the Iron Man suit. Many think that suit is all he has. In this issue, we'll see how Tony Stark fares without it.

31.text: Brian regains his Captain Britain powers just in time as Mastermind moves his plan for Omniverse dominance into its endgame.

33.text: You've asked for it! You've demanded it! But will you like it when we answer your questions? Spider-Man faces his future and his past head-on when a surprise turns his life upside down. But what does fate hold for the wall-crawler? Life? Love? Happiness? This is it, folks!

35.text: The Hulk discovers his soft side as he seeks acceptance for what, and who, he is...

38.text: Kraven the Hunter shows up at the doorstep of Xavier’s School for Gifted Youngsters, but he does not seek to cause any trouble. Except for one little thing…hopes of a battle with the Beast!

39.text: Blink has encountered a mysterious stranger in an even stranger land. Is he friend or foe?

41.text: It's a no-holds-barred, all-out battle between the Hulk and his hated dark twin, the Abomination!

42.text: While Moonknight battles the Assasins of Set-Thor, Captain Mar-Vell, the Hulk, and the X-Men are all mysteriously teleported to Egypt to watch the furious engagement! Plus, the final stand of the Fantastic Four.

43.text: Natasha comes face-to-face with herself. Disguised as Natasha, Yelena Belova takes on the original Black Widow in a face-off of ultimate espionage. Who will prove to be a better Natasha Romanoff?

44.text: Magneto and his mutant terrorist cell are preparing to follow through on their threats of Homo Sapien genocide.  Are the X-Men up to the task of stopping them?

46.text: Blink is now one of Magneto's X-Men. But being a team player was never her strong suit! Can Blink fall in line and be a good soldier or is she doomed to play the solo act?

47.text: It's Spider-Man versus the Green Goblin in their first battle ever.  And the battleground is Peter's high school!

50.text: A student saves his teacher! Skin rescues Sean Cassidy from an ambush, and Sean later learns Moira MacTaggert's fate.

52.text: A job goes horribly wrong as Deadpool fails to prevent the death of an innocent man! Now he must care for the man's son, who takes up the sidekick mantle of Pool Boy!

59.text: With Scourge on the loose, Hawkeye sets a new plan in motion for the Thunderbolts to finally catch and defeat their long-time foe! But an unexpected surprise awaits them back at HQ…

61.text: It's Round Two for Echo and Daredevil. Will Echo reign supreme or will DD get the best of her? Meanwhile, Foggy Nelson is getting along swimmingly without Kingpin mucking things up for him.

62.text:
Get ready for the fight you thought you'd never see: Cloak vs. Dagger!
And as the battle between former partners rages on in our world, the
Marvel Knights must escape from Cloak's dimension of darkness.

Get ready for the fight you thought you'd never see: Cloak vs. Dagger! And as the battle between former partners rages on in our world, the Marvel Knights must escape from Cloak's dimension of darkness.

64.text: Nick Fury accuses X-Force of playing on the Russians' team. Cannonball and Boom-Boom are Warpath's only shot at survival.

66.text: Thor must do battle with Nullitor-a robot sent from the future to destroy the Odinson. Meanwhile, a mysterious woman dressed like Thor appears. Is she friend or foe? Find out here!

67.text: Iron Man definitely has a hectic past, but what happens when it comes back to bite him back in the present?

69.text: The new Excalibur team heads into Otherworld to prevent Roma from completing her dominance over the Omniverse. Brian Braddock races to find the Sword of Might but finds a startling person guarding it!

70.text: With an intergalactic empire headed by the Shi'ar and the Kree on the verge of conquering the galaxy, Captain Marvel gives them 7 days to get their affairs in order... because he's going to kill them all!  32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$2.99

71.text: Cable becomes the target of an attack from the Dark Sisterhood!

72.text: When Gods Fall! Thor teams with comrades Beta Ray Bill and the Prince of Power Hercules to withstand the onslaught of Desak, the Destroyer of Gods!

73.text: An amazing Cerebro reading may lead the X-Men to a brand new mutant!

74.text: If you're a fan of the FF (and who isn't), this is the issue for you: Dr. Doom! Crystal! The Sub-Mariner! The Kree Sentry! The Fantasti-Car! An all-star cast of creators delivers all-out action in the Mighty Marvel Manner!

76.text: The wall-crawler and the Man Without Fear face the unlikely and unholy alliance of Owl, Gladiator, Copperhead and Stiltman! Which foe has a secret, and how might it spell doom for Spider-Man and Daredevil?

81.text: Natasha Romanoff begins her mission as Yelena Belova. She quickly discovers that her true identity may be under fire sooner than she thinks as she comes face-to-face with the real Yelena Belova, disguised as Natasha!

82.text: Spider-Man leaps into action for the first time!  But can he juggle a super hero life, a secret identity and high school all at the same time?

83.text: Deadpool is on the rebound after his recent romantic trouble. Will a series of attractive women help mend his broken heart?

85.text: Mar-Vell sets out to kill Death itself! Plus, Thor versus Loki and the appearance of an all new Ant-Man!

91.text: Moonstone is taken captive by Mentor and ISAAC! Can the Thunderbolts save her before her power source is completely drained?

93.text: THE RETURN OF K’UN-LUN PART 4 The fiery conclusion is here! Many of Marvel’s mightiest have gathered in Tokyo to prevent Junzo Muto from becoming the next Iron Fist incarnate. But have their efforts been in vain? Featuring Iron Man, Psylocke, and the agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.! Iron Fist must make the toughest decision of his life; no reader will want to miss this climactic finale!

95.text: Excalibur returns with an all-new team - Captain Britain, Psylocke, Black Knight, Meggan and Captain U.K.! When Otherworld attacks Captain Britain on Earth, he assembles a new team to take the fight back to Otherworld.

96.text: While on a shopping trip, Monet and Jubilee are bombarded by anti-mutant terrorists on the New York City subway!

98.text: The Vanisher is running drugs out Cuba causing unrest in America among the suburban youth. It's up to a team of X-Men with the help of SHIELD to stop him.

99.text: Our X-Men were able to fend off Dazzler, but not without Angel's mother ending up in critical condition…
